text: Sandun Dias (born 29 July 1985) is a Sri Lankan cricketer. He made his first- class debut for Nondescripts Cricket Club in the 2003–04 Premier Trophy on 14 November 2003. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Sri Lankan cricketers Category:Galle Cricket Club cricketers Category:Negombo Cricket Club cricketers Category:Tamil Union Cricket and Athletic Club cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
